[
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "This example demonstrates how to define your own tab panel component (that renders content depending on the selected tab) in an accessible way. "
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "For each tab panel, it is necessary to add the following attributes:"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "unordered-list",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "id",
                "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
              },
              {
                "text": " - necessary for defining which tab controls which tab panel (see the tab's attributes below)"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "role",
                "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
              },
              {
                "text": " - defines accessibility role"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item-child",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "aria-labelledby",
                "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
              },
              {
                "text": " - necessary for defining which tab labels which tab panel"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "For each tab, it is necessary to add "
      },
      {
        "text": "aria-controls",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " attribute with the value of a tab panel's "
      },
      {
        "text": "id",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " it controls."
      }
    ]
  }
]